<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #f6f9fc; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
    .logo { color: #1a56db; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px; text-decoration: none; }
    .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #888; margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea; padding-top: 20px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #1a56db; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; margin-top: 20px; }
    .highlight { color: #111827; font-weight: 600; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">Proteccio CMS</div>
    
    <h2 style="color: #111827; margin-top: 0;">Your Data Request is Ready</h2>
    
    <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
    <p>We have processed your data subject access request. Your personal data package is now ready for secure download.</p>
    
    <p>This package contains a comprehensive record of your <span class="highlight">consents, rights requests, and grievances</span> stored in our system, in accordance with DPDP/GDPR regulations.</p>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{downloadUrl}}" class="btn">Download Your Data (JSON)</a>
    </div>

    <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
      <strong>Note:</strong> For your security, this link will expire in 7 days. Please ensure you download and store your data securely.
    </p>

    <p>If you did not make this request, please contact our Data Protection Officer immediately.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{year}} Proteccio Data Privacy. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
